name: Event Open, FtC Open
description: The text is a summary of a crypto event called Fund in the Commons. The event focuses on creating an incubation ecosystem for funding public goods infrastructure. It includes workshop stages, an art gallery, and a parallel conference hosted by the Foresight Institute. Surprise speakers and announcements are expected throughout the day. The event takes place at Sorbonne University, with lunch served at 1 pm. The next speaker is Jeff Pulver.
